| Feature           | **Amazon ECR**                   | **JFrog Artifactory**               |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Type              | AWS-native container registry    | Enterprise artifact platform        |
| Ecosystem         | AWS-only                         | Multi-cloud + on-prem               |
| Integration       | Tight with EKS, IAM, VPC         | External integration required       |
| Setup             | Fully managed                    | Needs setup (SaaS/self-hosted)      |
| Artifact Support  | Containers only                  | Containers + Maven, npm, Helm, etc. |
| Security          | IAM-based, Inspector integration | Role-based + Xray integration       |
| CI/CD Integration | Basic                            | Advanced pipelines + automation     |
| UI/UX             | Basic                            | Rich developer-friendly UI          |
| Scalability       | Automatic                        | Depends on deployment               |
